				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote23-14445_002_039"><a name="23-14445_002_039"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote23-14445_002_039">23.</a></span>
					<p class=""><a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/nt/mark/5.36?lang=spa#35" target="_blank">Marcos 5:36</a>.</p>
